{"tid":1692621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(傷亡慘重)以後唔好再叫全民和理非 因為和勇係永不分","createTime":"2019-11-04T07:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T12:23:56.000Z","uid":124247,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"464369c79eb9bf8ff831d1421c9f5c3ff48abf1e","tid":1692621,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:21:03.000Z","msg":"相信經過琴日一晚 大家都可以見到 就算全民和理非<br />\n拖手唱歌<br />\nd狗要衝入商場拉人就拉人 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有商場都已經唔安全 唔再係保護罩</span></span><br />\n點解d狗琴日咁放肆衝入商場？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為一個勇武都冇</span></span><br />\n佢地連tg都唔洗放 想點拉就點拉<br />\n希望各位和理非<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住呢個慘痛既教訓</span></span><br />\n由今日開始 咩活動都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再有和理非叫勇武休息<br />\n唔好再叫勇武唔袋gear出黎<br />\n唔好再有和理非怨勇武比藉口狗清場<br />\n因為狗幾時拉人已經係控制唔到<br />\n和 勇 係 永 不 分 <br />\n同 時 並 肩 作 戰</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdGPRLT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdGPRLT.jpg&h=3680458d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCaMT26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCaMT26.jpg&h=abe00c5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"368a7fb00769e23e087637c6313599dca6133c61","tid":1692621,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:21:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望梓樂快d醒翻"},{"pid":"27fa3718fc24575af3dfbafb0e224dd9ed2d7279","tid":1692621,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"希望被斬夫婦平安無事"},{"pid":"3cb93e8d8d12216f8eb94db7d254aa09d98cd623","tid":1692621,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"希望成頭血手足平安出黎"},{"pid":"238a626395435a20a9992d813de62fd760d53866","tid":1692621,"uid":124247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"r